column16: Ty Wigginton grounds into double play, third baseman Wes Helms to second baseman Dan Uggla to first baseman Gaby Sanchez.    Nick Markakis out at 2nd.

Cesar Izturis out on a sacrifice bunt, catcher Ronny Paulino to second baseman Dan Uggla.    Craig Tatum to 2nd.

Jake Fox grounds out, third baseman Wes Helms to first baseman Gaby Sanchez.
